{
  "stem": "20609.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother-- I don't know how she did it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She even made me a suit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she didn't have any black material like-- the tradition was always for a kid to wear black at the bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she found some white material.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So this was the first time I-- I-- [LAUGHS] the first time the rabbi said this is unusual, you know, in his speech.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- I remember the rabbi.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His name was Levy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I got a picture of him that I found.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so she had a party at the house for around 30, 40 people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I have no idea where she got that food from.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had-- I mean, this was like unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's like being in heaven again with all the food, with the cakes and everything there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and this was probably the last time-- I didn't know it at that time-- this was basically the last time we all were together.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, my sister was not there because she was already deported to Poland, right?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] at that time, we were fairly left alone, personally, because my father still had a Polish passport, and he was still considered a foreign subject.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so when the war started, September 1 in 1939, he was arrested with all-- with many, many Jews, and mostly Poles.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And whatever they could find, they arrested and put them in the-- in the concentration camp near Berlin called Sachsenhausen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's also one of the first concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
